notes: |
  v0.1.0 ships the audit framework + safetensors-only SAE loader supporting
  the GPT-2 small (SAELens) and Pythia (EleutherAI sparsify) families out of
  the box; Llama Scope (fnlp) and Gemma Scope (google) load via the same path
  once their cfg keys are pinned. Goodfire DeepSeek-R1, Goodfire Llama 3.x
  Instruct, Qwen-Scope, and Gemma Scope 2 adapters await upstream safetensors
  re-export (or a community conversion adapter) and land in v0.1.1+. v0.1.0
  runs the audit pipeline in synthetic `demo_mode=True` only; real-model
  inference (forward-hook + SAE encode + benchmark loop) lands in v0.1.1+.
